race.comment: GRAMERCY GARRY (3) is a consistent dog overall, in the frame at two of 11 starts including six wins but missed the frame latest when fifth (30.04) over 520m at Wentworth Park. Form here sound including four wins. Happy to have him on top this line-up. NOEMIE (1) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on her quick win the start prior, getting around Wentworth Park over 520m in 29.84. Should be in this for a long way. PELOPONNESE (7) is having her first look at this course. Comes here after a last start 4th and beaten 4.5 lengths (29.93) at Wentworth Park. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. ROYAL PANAMA (5) can find the frame without surprising.
